title: VTEN, Sacar & Mr. D Live in London – Nepali New Year 2083
description: Get ready to witness history as we celebrate Nepali New Year 2083 with a monumental concert. For the first time ever, VTEN, Sacar (Lil Buddha), and Mr. D come together for the biggest collaboration in Nepali Hip-Hop history. Experience the energy, the bars, and the culture live in London. Tickets are officially live — secure your spot now before they’re gone.

title: LG Fest-UK 2026 (Sabin Rai & The Pharaoh, Kandara, Purna Rai & Dajubhaiharu, Ekdev Limbu, Jay Author)
venue: Rushmoor Arena, Fleet Rd, Aldershot GU11 2ET
description: LG Fest-UK 2026 is a one-day outdoor Nepalese music & culture festival at Rushmoor Arena, Aldershot (12:00–22:00). Live performances, authentic Nepalese food stalls, and community celebration. Line-up includes Sabin Rai & The Pharaoh, Kandara, Purna Rai & Dajubhaiharu, Ekdev Limbu, and Jay Author. Important: 18+ only, no re-entry, tickets final sale.
